Dialogue: 0,1:44:32.08,1:44:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,of all existence.\NAnd
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.44,1:44:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,between the thoughts, under the thoughts\Nis the profound silence. And all we have
Dialogue: 0,1:44:42.63,1:44:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to do is become aware of that silence.\NAll we have to do is become aware of
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.00,1:45:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that silence by realizing it's there.\NBehind all the sound of the universe,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.92,1:46:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the silence is forever there.\NBehind the sounds in the woods, in the
Dialogue: 0,1:46:03.92,1:46:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,woods are silent.\NThe sound of the bird
Dialogue: 0,1:46:09.44,1:46:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't have anything to do with the\Nsilence. You see the silence
Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.63,1:46:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,is maintained\Neven though there's sound above it but
Dialogue: 0,1:46:19.04,1:46:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the only reason you can hear the sound\Nis because it against the background of
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.56,1:46:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,silence. So the silence is there right\Nin the middle of sound. So you focus on
Dialogue: 0,1:46:27.19,1:46:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the on the silence which is everpresent\Nin the middle of cacaphony and
Dialogue: 0,1:46:33.60,1:46:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,catastrophe as the bullets are flying\Naround and the planes are crashing and
Dialogue: 0,1:46:37.28,1:46:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,all hell is breaking loose and there's\Nnothing but the infinite silence.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.28,1:46:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So you identify with that silence and\Njust maintain awareness. You can go
Dialogue: 0,1:46:50.23,1:46:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,about your daily life and do everything\Nthat you need to do and at all times
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.56,1:46:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,still be aware of the presence of the\Nsilence.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.48,1:47:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So that gives you a centering. So a a\Ncentering kind of prayerfulness is
Dialogue: 0,1:47:06.08,1:47:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you're always aware of the silence which\Nis the infinite context. The reality of
Dialogue: 0,1:47:10.23,1:47:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the presence of God is an infinite\Nsilence.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:13.84,1:47:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And then that which you hold in mind in\Nthat silence tends to manifest
Dialogue: 0,1:47:19.28,1:47:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,not as a result of causation\Nbut potentiality manifesting.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:28.08,1:47:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And we thank thee oh Lord for thy divine\Npresence as the infinite silence out of
Dialogue: 0,1:47:32.15,1:47:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,which arises our existence.\NAmen.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:39.44,1:47:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, that was a pretty fancy prayer,\Nwasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.84,1:48:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. It's my joy to be with you again\Nand I look forward to our next meeting.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:05.44,1:48:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And we finish with the same we started.\NGloria and Excelsius Dio.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:10.96,1:48:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We thank thee, oh Lord, for thy divine\Npresence.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:14.63,1:48:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You are my gift. You're my gift from\NGod.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:19.36,1:48:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, God.\NEveryone here is my presence from God, I
Dialogue: 0,1:48:26.96,1:48:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,tell you.\NYeah. What a blessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:33.19,1:48:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What a blessing. Look at these gorgeous\Nflowers. Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:38.23,1:48:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Gorgeous.\NHallelujah.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:51.04,1:49:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallelujah.\NHallelujah.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:13.36,1:49:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallelujah.\NHallelujah.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:42.88,1:50:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallelujah.\NHallelujah.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:12.40,1:50:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallelujah.\NHallelu
Dialogue: 0,1:50:43.11,1:50:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallelu.
